  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Most developers have no clue Anthropic shipped a real skill ecosystem.",
      "checksum": "sha256:aa13bbbcc6a73d64741a4f9f366d89647a08d6ded71605475297ef925fde97dc",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "And five of these skills are eating GitHub right now.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0a66677934daf1b053f53842fb896d277e54951466bf0749a74ae216fce7b1aa",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "The numbers are insane. Five skills. Three hundred sixty thousand weekly installs combined. The official Anthropic skills repository just crossed one hundred thirty two thousand stars on GitHub.",
      "checksum": "sha256:263cbe0fc6eeca762bfc019fd5292bc9e1e9c3d73bb7c6e9fc54e2cefd7c73f1",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 12.26013605442177,
      "word_count": 28,
      "words_offset": 21
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Fifteen thousand five hundred forks. Thousands of public skills published in five months.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2a2a3d400121e4064805c2fc90f38f3633e8382c8adc1096ef8c8bae69ad98c1",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 49
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Most devs are still asking what a skill even is.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5a8dedf3c9b0b51e8e02d8f668616c9aca457f614317767ebb1da5aefa91c3fc",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 62
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "So which five are actually blowing up? Number one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e781f12093782a1c972982926c707db5fcde67f73f96e374f441e0566f3a0616",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 72
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Frontend Design. One hundred ten thousand weekly installs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:92c33eb3336c226f0adf26d51d3f1b2a9d650e3b2e4d062f9cc43525cb821591",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 81
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "This is the skill that fixes vibe-coded UIs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3e966637c7fbdc1b877d796f6429ff11e6ff31f22e76ba4d725896bf016d9f0b",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 89
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "It hands Claude a real design system before it touches a single line of code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:93017ccf9b504538052faac5f5bcbf38809f1a299b71b6d782af269ae3a34b1e",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 97
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Distinctive typography. Purposeful color palettes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d425b636a8c699bc949a6299a27507be952eb33d364951a2e182ef71f963ec54",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 112
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Animation that feels intentional, not decorative.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c33f60669d99f9d0fa0a63d1386704c4a347cb94aab4f243b9de663deb35f69a",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 117
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Every dev tired of generic A I slop installed this one first.",
      "checksum": "sha256:90d7f36ae77f18145b706890bec717877ed7b060fee508bf3c2a8e517598b754",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 123
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Number two. Superpowers. One hundred eighty seven thousand stars on GitHub.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ea72fe66c07319b3412b0dea855f3a649b219b8d88cdcdcbfd64b0888f6a4c6d",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 5.2477097505668935,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 135
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Sixteen thousand forks. This is the skill that turns Claude into a planning agent.",
      "checksum": "sha256:04b1f21878527f7445157f7481cc33990d128e8f4124a6dc15f2857dd641b93e",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 146
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "It runs structured multi-step development with subagents and test-driven workflows.",
      "checksum": "sha256:07cc02ad067e76111cff060a87863caf82b510e10b2353aad7b11f3911453597",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 160
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Vibe coding, but the code actually compiles, tests, and ships.",
      "checksum": "sha256:293dca76c2b654f67494b72f2b2a3d2a9b5b21b3973bfe49ed4648bcf24a0f96",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 170
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Number three. Remotion Best Practices. One hundred seventeen thousand weekly installs since February.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3cd0025c616c40bae902508c74df1bd89968bf2dafcf8b10b4a9f14d137672e2",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 6.826666666666667,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 180
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Remotion is the React framework that lets you generate video programmatically.",
      "checksum": "sha256:11fb183ed36d3ee781372a2d5635480bea2be4f9fd80f411e300f1b27d5a5c99",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 193
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "This skill teaches Claude every gotcha. Now Claude can write a full video pipeline that actually renders.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b3568aac1df52af47611af1ed5b5fb85a678058a3e336377414c539cd70c65fd",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 6.594467120181406,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 204
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "From one prompt. Number four. Vercel Web Design Guidelines.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bd4bfc2f2bc2d75d7003ebcc6c1be1159444f0b912f4d06300d4b48acd7843f1",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 221
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "One hundred thirty three thousand weekly installs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ba6250c686ea3137fd537c55607d4d0e68533567e8012f258326edad6663c2a8",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 230
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "It audits your interface against more than a hundred accessibility and user-experience rules.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4d0a69f0a9be93b8709c74e32d5456158f871a9288d7eb29ff010f7098ecdaf9",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 5.154829931972789,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 237
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "The exact playbook Vercel uses inside Vercel.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a3c63834fd7fb2c6a7d5767ce95e5673896c3fbb99d9c487a9fa1c7c324bef86",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 2.6006349206349206,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 250
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "Plug it in and every page Claude builds passes a real production audit.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f443e06bf9437369d31b47955855724d1e9d1ac15acb40767f4c207528082b69",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 257
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Number five. Skill Creator. Anthropic's own meta-skill.",
      "checksum": "sha256:852027c9de0e8a321975b5152758209ea4a2bcf0ad7d08d27e550696808d2680",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 270
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "You answer a few interactive questions and it generates a complete custom skill for you.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d51ea809b19bd6c232833652ff28063b5f736d8b2a0ce9867f00319c719c1162",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 277
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "With proper frontmatter. With instructions.",
      "checksum": "sha256:27dd19b92548347b5b8c877f21e1ce01fde7f6c30c96ddbc46a6276531c390e3",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 292
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "Ready to install. A factory that builds factories.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5d0706a1b6d208cf48184ac4454dd859d2850a811958987ccaa63c3464469204",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 297
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "And it ships free. This is not toy stuff.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f66a9dc00a2544da1346cbed3c5c106cb219ff7f3a9de39e087e5cad2a4a64c2",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 305
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "The same skill format already runs on Claude Code, Codex, Gemini, Cursor, and Copilot.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1d8ad4deed2547dddb3011a4174100ecdbe76fb349e9d5600d8c3a47f8edddb1",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 5.38702947845805,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 314
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "Vercel ships the open skills tool at skills dot S H.",
      "checksum": "sha256:06eb525c48f7c8cb291bb376c0bee6fdc7614b8bea9af08c7efa35ad216b3497",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 328
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "Eighteen thousand stars on GitHub. Skills are not a side project.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7ada66c36a2379e1280705818261911d596bd7f0d750a60d8a9215c1aa685d8a",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 339
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "The skill is the new S D K. Did you know all of them?",
      "checksum": "sha256:3d2d3362a08479d934113d72a6c297548e67c0dbe62689194ac5c830ca840eac",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 350
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "Let me know in the comments. If you want to learn more about A I, check out the dynamous dot AI community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4e6632aa1790c8d9dd9913e94c0e67c848c0dcfe9c3cea597a0cba7ff720db0e",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 5.990748299319728,
